Repository Name Unauthorized: Alabama Space and Rocket Center Archives
Notes: The Space and Rocket Center Archives collects historical and current materials related to missiles and the space program.  Holdings consist of approximately 500,000 manuscripts, photographs, maps, and printed items.  Dr. Wernher von Braun, Colonel Leslie A. Skinner, General Holgar N Toftoy, and General John A. Barclay are among the individuals whose activities are documented.
Source of Repository Data: Alabama Department of Archives and History
